[url=https://news.blizzard.com/en-us/blizzard/21098852/new-social-features-now-in-beta-in-the-blizzard-battle-net-desktop-app?locale=en-us]Източник[/url]</description></item><item><title>Diablo IV: Vessel of Hatred</title><link>https://www.d3bg.org/forum/showpost.php?groupid=11&amp;catid=37&amp;postid=7380&amp;page=10</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 00:34:51 +0300</pubDate><updated>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:51:54 +0200</updated><description>Появиха се първите слухове за първия експанжън на играта. Били качили &amp;quot;Version 2&amp;quot; на играта с номер 2.0.0[color=#d80909]ta[/color].45667, което се предполага, че може би става въпрос за Technical Alpha. Близкон е само след месец, да видим дали ще го обяват. :)

[link]https://www.wowhead.com/news/patch-2-0-on-cdn-hints-at-diablo-4-expansion-335300[/link]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/lQk6xQa.png[/img]</description></item><item><title>Диабло 4 впечатления</title><link>https://www.d3bg.org/forum/showpost.php?groupid=11&amp;catid=37&amp;postid=6982&amp;page=83</link><pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2019 03:08:26 +0200</pubDate><updated>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 14:53:35 +0200</updated><description>Честито. Обявиха ни Диабло 4, но изглежда няма да излезе скоро. Няма да е &amp;quot;дори Близард скоро&amp;quot;. Обещават ни да пускат ъпдейт на всеки 4 месеца за разработката на играта. Вероятно най-рано 2021. 

[bluepost]Hey all,

We’re very excited to reveal one of our most eagerly anticipated projects and have you all take a closer look at what’s next for Diablo.

This comes with a caveat; we’re still a way out from launch. Because we’re heads down in development, we’re not launching a dedicated forum for Diablo IV yet.

However, we still want you to feel welcome to discuss the game amongst yourselves. While we may not be able to answer all your burning questions, we are committed to sharing updates with the community and participating when we can.

Beginning next year, we will be providing quarterly updates regarding the progress of Diablo IV’s development. This might take the form of a blog or a developer post here, which we’ll sticky and leave open for ongoing discussion until the next update is available.

We’ll also keep an updated table of contents of all updates in this post so you’ll have a convenient place to refer to them over the course of development. We’ve included all the news coming out of this weekend so far to get you started.[/bluepost]</description></item></channel></rss> 